21:15:03 INFO    bt5151_credit_risk.graph        Num_of_Delayed_Payment: String numeric with tail artifacts like '8_'. Strip, cap at 120, fill per customer.
21:15:03 INFO    bt5151_credit_risk.graph        Changed_Credit_Limit: Percent change stored as string, '_' sentinel 2 091 rows. After cleaning values cluster −20–20 so cap ±100. Stable per c
21:15:03 INFO    bt5151_credit_risk.graph        Num_Credit_Inquiries: p99 = 1 109 but realistic domain <100. Outlier removal then customer median.
